---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | latepaycalc.com';
const description = 'How latepaycalc.com handles your data.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 10, 2026.</em></p>
  <p>latepaycalc.com is operated by The Click Lab. We take privacy seriously and write our policy in plain language.</p>
  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <p>Calculator inputs are processed in your browser only &mdash; we don't transmit or store them. We use Google Analytics to understand which pages are popular; this collects general information like country and device type, not identifying information.</p>
  <h2>Cookies and advertising</h2>
  <p>Google AdSense cookies serve ads based on your prior visits. Opt out via <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Ads Settings</a>.</p>
  <h2>Third parties</h2>
  <p>We don't sell or share your data beyond the analytics and advertising services described above.</p>
  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>EU/UK/California residents have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data. Since we don't collect identifying data, there's typically nothing to access. Contact us via <a href="/contact">our contact page</a>.</p>
  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>Material changes announced via banner on the homepage.</p>
</BaseLayout>
